<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Soulfire</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">2H Slash</a><BR>
Damage per second - 10.44<BR>
Damage 23 - Delay 45<BR>
Weight: 5.0 - DWF, ERU, HIE, HUM<BR>
Classes: <a href="/paladin/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">PAL</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/complete_healing.shtml?spellID=291">Complete Healing</a><BR>
Charges: 5<BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(STR +7) (WIS +7) </font>
<BR>
Submitted By: Chris B.<BR>

