<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>What faction does Brother Hayle in Splitpaw( the guy you turn the Hilt,<BR>
Brilliant Sword of Faith, and Testimony into)belong to? Some<BR>
faction in Qeynos I am guessing? If you know the answer to this<BR>
please post it along with a quest or two that will raise faction<BR>
with him if possible. Also, what faction is needed with him<BR>
to be able to complete the quest? (indiff, amiable, etc.)<BR>
<BR>
Thanks!<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
39th paladin<BR>
Fennin Ro</font></td></tr></table>
