<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I was actually involved in beating down Lucan to help a guild mate get a Soulfire and he does NOT, I repeat, DOES NOT have lay hands. We jumped him with 2 groups of 40s. Four of which were paladins with Soulfires already, hehe. We also had rangers, bards, and monks fighting as well. I'm a 39 bard. A cleric was also present to help heal as he hits for hell of a lot of damage! We gave him a good trashing and the fight lasted about 2 minutes. He didn't lay hands at all and was never healed a considerable amount.  We beat down his 2 friends in a few minutes as well. Good luck to you other paladins in giving that filthy militia a good ol' fashioned beatdown. Don't worry about being KOS in freeport. Just use the sewers. Besides Freeport is a dump anyways. </font></td></tr></table>
