<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Ganeldil Darkbane</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-18 16:34:10</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white><BR>
Lucan does not have LoH, and You can count on Brother Coming from the militia house to help him, even if you wait for Gentry to return to his home point by hailing Lucan, Lucan is very tough and has about 10K hit points in his human form and only about 5K as the second incarnation. A 55th level Ogre SK was getting whacked real good by Lucan and required considerable healing, this was after Lucan killed a 41 and 33 Ranger in no time. We put him down though, and here was are configuration<BR>
<BR>
55 Ogre SK<BR>
54 Human Pally<BR>
37 Human Pally<BR>
41 Woodie Ranger<BR>
33 Woodie Ranger<BR>
40 Troll SK<BR>
39 Woodie Druid<BR>
<BR>
When Gentry got back to the Militia House we began the assault on Lucan way out by the Ecommons zone against the wall the sewers are on. Farthest possible point from the Brother Gentry, Brother Gentry still came, The 54 Paladin and the 40th SK interecepted him before he could heal Lucan, the rest of us stayed on Lucan, with the exception of the 39 Druid who was kiting another Guard that showed up.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Ganeldil Darkbane<BR>
37th lvl Knight of Truth<BR>
